title: I received two skins I never bought.
body:
I just noticed I received 2 skins on december 1st, they are Grey Warwick and Lunar Wraith Morgana.
I'd just like to know if this is normal?

replies.body: So that Grey Warwick skin most likely came from getting Honor Rank 5 and opening that capsule! The Lunar Wraith Morgana skin you got from rerolling 3 skins to get a random permanent skin.
